fun main(args: Array<String>) {
    val sequence = generateSequence(1) { it + 1 }.take(100)
    val squareOfSums = squareOfSums(sequence)
    val sumOfSquares = sumOfSquares(sequence)
    println(squareOfSums - sumOfSquares)
}

fun sumOfSquares(sequence: Sequence<Int>) = sequence.map { it * it }.sumOfInt()

fun squareOfSums(sequence: Sequence<Int>) = sequence.sumOfInt() * sequence.sumOfInt()
